reviewText: This guided project is not for beginners who want to learn how to create printables, using Canva. This Course would better serve beginners by using simple fonts, and colors, and providing slower instruction for those who are learning both the Canva features as well as how to create the printables. The course is too short per module for those such as myself who are learning the features of Canva and learning to create printables at the same time. This course requires familarity with the software program being used to create said printables.
Make more of these. They are great courses. Thank you.
